-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00f2ng 33 Premier League \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u00e0n l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Man City vs MU 2-3 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">0 &ndash; Man United kh\u00f4ng tung ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o trong hi\u1ec7p 1, l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t h\u1ecd tr\u1ea3i qua \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2015, tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh Man City.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">0 &ndash; Man United kh\u00f4ng tung ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch n\u00e0o trong hi\u1ec7p 1, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n sau 4 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 2.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1 &ndash; Trong 50 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Man City \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t Paul Pogba l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2 &ndash; Pogba l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a MU l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Man City t\u1ea1i Premier League, sau Rooney v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2012.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Man City vs MU\" title=\"Pogba Man City vs MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/Thang-nguoc-Man-City-2-3-MU,-Mou-tien-the-to-Pep-la-ke-doi-tra-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Man City vs MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n2 &ndash; Vincent Kompany ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2/23 tr\u1eadn derby Manchester, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y anh kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap Man City tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch nh\u01b0 l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc (2012).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2 &ndash; Jose Mourinho c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pep Guardiola, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn Barca 1-2 Real Madrid (2012).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2 &ndash; Alexis Sanchez c\u00f3 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean anh l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Premier League, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 12/2014 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 &ndash; \u0110\u00e3 3 n\u0103m k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb 2015, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola m\u1edbi thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1 &ndash; L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola thua 2 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">9 &ndash; Trong 9 tr\u1eadn Smalling ho\u1eb7c Pogba ghi b\u00e0n, Man United \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Ryan Babel (11 b\u00e0n \u0111em l\u1ea1i 11 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng) l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba v\u00e0 Smalling l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn Man City vs MU\" title=\"Pogba v\u00e0 Smalling l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/smal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba v\u00e0 Smalling l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n cho Man United</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n23 &ndash; V\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n thua trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, David De Gea \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 23 b\u00e0n thua k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a Premier League. \u0110\u00e1ng n\u00f3i, theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 &ldquo;b\u00e0n th\u1eafng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng&rdquo;, s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 37 b\u00e0n, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">39 &ndash; L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong 39 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Premier League, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kevin De Bruyne kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">97 &ndash; Kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Pogba l\u00e0 97 gi\u00e2y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">400 &ndash; \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 400 c\u1ee7a Ashley Young trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2008 &ndash; L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2008 Man City m\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, sau tr\u1eadn thua Liverpool 2-3 (th\u00e1ng 10/2008).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div><strong>T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 chung cu\u1ed9c<br>\r\n</strong> &nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Man City vs MU: 2-3<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>Ghi b\u00e0n<br>\r\n</strong> &nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Man City: Kompany (25&rsquo;), Gundogan (31&rsquo;)</div>\r\n<div>MU: Pogba (53&rsquo;, 55&rsquo;), Smalling (69&rsquo;)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Man City vs MU 2-3</div>\r\n<div><span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/11830134/013100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Man City 2-3 MU</span></div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265774\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/04/08/highlight-man-city-vs-man-utd-vong-33-nha.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-diem-nhan-tran-cau-kinh-dien-man-city-vs-mu-172-183765.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/8/r