bf \u0111ang nghi\u00eang h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh London.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>Arsenal \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ed3i gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/arsenal-4.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Arsenal </strong></span>\u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i CSKA Moscow v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-1 trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Europa League. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal vs Southampton (20h15 ngay 0804) Nghien nat ke khon cung hinh anh\" title=\"Arsenal vs Southampton (20h15 ng\u00e0y 0804) Nghi\u1ec1n n\u00e1t k\u1ebb kh\u1ed1n c\u00f9ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/Arsenal-vs-Southampton-(20h15-ngay-0804)-Nghien-nat-ke-khon-cung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/mesut-ozil-43842.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong> Mesut Ozil</strong></span> ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 linh h\u1ed3n trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi 5 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, trong \u0111\u00f3 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Ramsey v\u00e0 Lacazette b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 khi m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc CSKA Moscow gi\u00fap Arsenal n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 5 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn. Sau 4 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Wenger \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. Nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y gi\u00fap h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec hy v\u1ecdng mong manh trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua Top 4.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i nay, Arsenal vs Southampton trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 33 Premier League. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 6, k\u00e9m Top 4 \u0111\u1ebfn 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 san l\u1ea5p trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n v\u00e0i v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London v\u1eabn h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Arsenal vs Southampton\" title=\"Preview Arsenal vs Southampton\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/Preview-Arsenal-vs-Southampton.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal vs Southampton \u1edf v\u00f2ng 33 Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nH\u1ecd c\u1ea7n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u00e2m l\u00fd t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. Ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n b\u1ecb g\u00f2 b\u00f3 b\u1edfi th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng \u0111ang gi\u00fap Arsenal ch\u01a1i thanh tho\u00e1t h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n, c\u00e1c pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p s\u1eafc n\u00e9t h\u01a1n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Wenger s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 Lacazette, Ozil hay Ramsey ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal vs Southampton, song Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Aubameyang, ng\u01b0\u1eddi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh thay Lacazette \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Premier League anh g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, bao g\u1ed3m 5 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Wilshere hay Welbeck c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u1eaft HLV Gareth Southgate, \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 VCK World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Southampton \u0111ang r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi Arsenal th\u0103ng hoa th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/southampton-1148.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Southampton</strong></span> thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Trong 20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Premier League h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 tr\u1eadn. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n St Mary \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf c\u1ea3 kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u1eabn ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7, h\u1ecd trong s\u1ed1 31 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ecd h\u00f2a t\u1edbi 13 l\u1ea7n, Southampton l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Southampton dang choi that vong trong thoi gian gan day\" title=\"Southampton \u0111ang ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/southampton.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Southampton \u0111ang ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nNh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Southampton \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 West Ham hay Newcastle, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng \u0111ang trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, song trong hai tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n St Mary \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 thua. 3 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Premier League, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n thua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ea9y Southampton xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 18 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi nh\u00f3m an to\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eb3ng ai ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ng\u1eafn kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi nh\u00f3m x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Mark Hughes \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc. Ngay trong tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi tr\u1eafng tay tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-3. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Mark Hughes c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 xoay chuy\u1ec3n t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rat kho de Southampton gay bat ngo truoc Arsenal\" title=\"R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 Southampton g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/southampton-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 Southampton g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Southampton t\u1eebng g\u00e2y r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho Arsenal. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, trong 10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed7i b\u00ean c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f9ng tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c nhau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Arsenal gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Stoke v\u00e0 Watford trong 2 v\u00f2ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec Southampton ch\u1ec9 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 thua trong 5 v\u00f2ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. X\u00e9t m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Wenger \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Arsenal vs Southampton\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Arsenal vs Southampton\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/Arsenal-vs-Southampton-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Arsenal vs Southampton</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: 3-1</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"te