}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t 2018, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i D\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u1ecdc T\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng may qua \u0111\u1eddi sau 5 ng\u00e0y \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9t qu\u1ef5.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mot trong tai qua doi sau dot kiem tra the luc VFF hinh anh\" title=\"M\u1ed9t tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i qua \u0111\u1eddi sau \u0111\u1ee3t ki\u1ec3m tra th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c VFF h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/Tan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i D\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u1ecdc T\u00e2n (tr\u00e1i) \u0111\u00e3 qua \u0111\u1eddi sau 5 ng\u00e0y \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb t\u1ea1i b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t 2018 c\u1ee7a VFF h\u00f4m 2/4 v\u1eeba qua, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i tr\u1ebb D\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u1ecdc T\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9t qu\u1ef5. \u00d4ng T\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o B\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n Xanh P\u00f4n c\u1ea5p c\u1ee9u sau \u0111\u00f3 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn B\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n B\u1ea1ch Mai.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean sau 5 ng\u00e0y n\u1eb1m vi\u1ec7n, t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng T\u00e2n ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn x\u1ea5u. V\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i 37 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 c\u00f5i \u0111\u1eddi t\u1ea1i b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n s\u00e1ng 7/4 v\u1eeba qua.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i D\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u1ecdc T\u00e2n qua \u0111\u1eddi \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 37 l\u00e0 m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gi\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u1ed9t tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam qua \u0111\u1eddi sau khi tham gia b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y, c\u00f2i v\u00e0ng 2006, c\u1ef1u tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i D\u01b0\u01a1ng M\u1ea1nh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfc ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p tr\u1ebb. \u00d4ng H\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u0169ng tr\u00e1ch c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i c\u1ee7a VFF gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i qua \u0111\u1eddi sau bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;S\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd D\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u1ecdc T\u00e2n c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp do s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 quan c\u1ee7a Ban tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i. T\u00f4i n\u00f3i th\u1eb3ng, h\u1ecd qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i qu\u00e1 v\u00f4 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m. T\u00f4i d\u1eabn ch\u1ee9ng nh\u00e9, th\u1eddi t\u00f4i c\u00f2n l\u00e0m, ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111i ki\u1ec3m tra m\u1eaft c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 l\u1ea7n.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i m\u1eaft k\u00e9m th\u00ec l\u00e0m sao m\u00e0 quan s\u00e1t t\u1ed1t ch\u1ee9. R\u1ed3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 v\u00f4 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi kh\u00f4ng theo d\u00f5i s\u00e1t sao v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y&rdquo;, \u00f4ng H\u00f9ng b\u1ee9c x\u00fac.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"891","checkdouble":"183749"},{"date":"22:07 07/04","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c d\u00e0nh cho T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/18/truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-ve-an-phat-cua-bau-duc-danh-cho-tang-tien.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bo