0T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t ki\u1ec1u \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i CH S\u00e9c, Tony Tu\u1ea5n Anh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tu\u1ea5n Anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean xa l\u1ea1 v\u1edbi NHM b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh t\u1eebng xin t\u1eadp nh\u1edd v\u1edbi \u0110T U20 Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t sang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Hoang Anh Tuan che sao Viet kieu trong doi hinh U19 Viet Nam hinh anh\" title=\"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n ch\u00ea sao Vi\u1ec7t ki\u1ec1u trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/0c5a0174_wwtk.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tony Tu\u1ea5n Anh c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf \u1edf l\u1ea7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee3t n\u00e0y, ng\u00f4i sao Vi\u1ec7t ki\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m trong m\u1eaft BHL U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tuy nhi\u00ean theo chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n th\u00ec Tony Tu\u1ea5n Anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cNgo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t, c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. V\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y Tu\u1ea5n Anh ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n\", v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam chia s\u1ebb.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u nay 7/4, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u00ec Ph\u00f9 \u0110\u1ed5ng FC. \u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, Tony Tu\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed ch\u01a1i trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 theo nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n th\u00ec anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea1m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng Tu\u1ea5n 'con' n\u00f3i: \u201cChi\u1ec1u nay, Tu\u1ea5n Anh ch\u01a1i trung v\u1ec7 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m. T\u00f4i x\u1ebfp Tony Tu\u1ea5n Anh ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng gian h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n xem k\u1ef9 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Tu\u1ea5n Anh nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. Tr\u1eadn chi\u1ec1u nay t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Tu\u1ea5n Anh ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U19 Suwon JS Cup di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb 18/4 \u0111\u1ebfn 22/4.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n \u1edf H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u00f2n hai \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n n\u1eefa t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tranh t\u00e0i t\u1ea1i VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Indonesia v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay.\u00a0<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"889","checkdouble":"183752"},{"date":"23:05 07/04","title":"9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn th\u01b0\u1edfng 1,8 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng sau ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/1/25/9-cau-thu-u23-viet-nam-nhan-thuong-18-ty-dong-sau-ngoi-a-quan-chau-luc.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{paddin