adn El Clasico \u1edf Camp Nou ng\u00e0y 6/5</span> v\u00e0 theo truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng, Real Madrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eadp h\u00e0nh r\u00e0o danh d\u1ef1 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n v\u00e0 ch\u00fac m\u1eebng nh\u00e0 t\u00e2n v\u01b0\u01a1ng La Liga.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Zidane quyet khong cho Real chuc mung Barca vo dich La Liga hinh anh\" title=\"HLV Zidane quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng cho Real ch\u00fac m\u1eebng Barca v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/zidane-quyet-khong-cho-real-chuc-mung-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Zidane quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng cho Real l\u1eadp h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o danh d\u1ef1 ch\u00fac m\u1eebng Barca v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u00ec s\u1ef1 th\u00f9 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u00e2u \u0111\u1eddi gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1eddi chung n\u00e0y, HLV Zinedine Zidane th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tinh th\u1ea7n fair-play \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n Barca v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cKh\u00f4ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u1eadp h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o danh d\u1ef1 ch\u00fac m\u1eebng h\u1ecd, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i r\u1ed3i. T\u1ea1i sao \u01b0? B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Barcelona c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e2u t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3 khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch FIFA Club World Cup h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i th\u00f4i. V\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y c\u0169ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u1ea3 th\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Barca v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n s\u1edbm mu\u1ed9n v\u00e0 Real Madrid ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh n\u00e9 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 l\u1eadp h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o danh d\u1ef1 ch\u00fac m\u1eebng t\u00e2n v\u01b0\u01a1ng La Liga, n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng\u2026 m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m trong v\u00f2ng m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 khi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Zidane gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ed3n to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c cho \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League, n\u01a1i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-juventus-03-real-madrid-gioi-han-nao-cho-ken-ken-trang-184-183492.html\">ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n h\u1ecd \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</span>.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/goc-real-madrid-vung-vang-va-chenh-venh-zidane-nguoi-di-tren-day-184-183441.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/goc-real-madrid-vung-vang-va-chenh-venh-zidane-nguoi-di-tren-day.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/goc-real-madrid-vung-vang-va-chenh-venh-zidane-nguoi-di-tren-day-184-183441.html\">G\u00f3c Real Madrid: V\u1eefng v\u00e0ng v\u00e0 ch\u00eanh v\u00eanh \u2013 Zidane ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i tr\u00ean d\u00e2y</span><br>\r\nHLV Zinedine Zidane ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i tr\u00ean d\u00e2y v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n ch\u00eanh v\u00eanh c\u00f9ng Real Madrid tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u1edf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nGia Khoa \u2013 B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"886","checkdouble":"183737"}]}